#: ../../developer/releases/3_0/release-notes.rst:3
#: d7cb161b98f24fad89219e959490ee13
msgid "Qubes R3.0 release notes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/3_0/release-notes.rst:7
#: f7e3ada753b046a1999af4ad34de90bf
msgid "This Qubes OS release is dedicated to the memory of Caspar Bowden."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/3_0/release-notes.rst:10
#: dd7c02ea9b5a4b4f874953678791e34e
msgid "New features since 2.0"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/3_0/release-notes.rst:13
#: f667f5fa1a5a4efe8b100236f39c4778
msgid ""
"HAL (Hypervisor Abstraction Layer) - based on libvirt, opens a whole new "
"possibilities of using different hypervisors. Currently Qubes OS uses Xen."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/3_0/release-notes.rst:15
#: 3701d6825f28486e947954023349a4f5
msgid ""
"Xen 4.4 - many new features, but for us the most important is much more "
"mature libxl toolstack."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/3_0/release-notes.rst:17
#: 5a3f5bd078ce4088bb106b7d6ef10c78
msgid ""
"Qrexec 3 - greatly improved performance by using direct VM-VM connections "
"and bigger buffers."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/3_0/release-notes.rst:19
#: 72b7ac0073d04265969459a7b70fd6c5
msgid "Debian templates gets official support."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/3_0/release-notes.rst:21
#: 931a3ca049c44e35bb34cb5b146292f0
msgid "Whonix templates"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/3_0/release-notes.rst:23
#: d30aaaba194d487b945b2eba5089bc33
msgid ""
"Build system improvements - especially support for distribution-specific "
"plugins (makes supporting multiple distributions much easier) and building "
"templates using DispVM."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/3_0/release-notes.rst:25
#: 5ab8ea8582c64b35a235e1c67c09af96
msgid ""
"Automated tests - makes much easier to find bugs, before its even shipped to"
" users"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/3_0/release-notes.rst:30
#: 8ba81d21d98d42688c20b44d5295a90e
msgid "Known issues"
msgstr "Problèmes connus"

#: ../../developer/releases/3_0/release-notes.rst:33
#: c5aa746f0deb4292bd5156cec31e5c7b
msgid "Windows Tools: ``qvm-block`` does not work"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/3_0/release-notes.rst:35
#: a2fbcee348814d6484f4f06fb715f416
msgid ""
"UEFI is not supported, you need to enable “legacy boot” in BIOS before "
"installing Qubes OS"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/3_0/release-notes.rst:37
#: 79d3ed64a96f4cc39d08185bd4f911ec
msgid ""
"Some icons in the Qubes Manager application might not be drawn correctly "
"when using the Xfce4 environment in Dom0. If this bothers you, please use "
"the KDE environment instead."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/3_0/release-notes.rst:39
#: 27ffab6347324b32bf934ddea781ab57
msgid ""
"If your GPU is not correctly supported by the Dom0 kernel (e.g. the 3D "
"desktop effects do not run smoothly) then you might experience “heaviness” "
"with Windows 7-based AppVMs. In that case, please solve the problem with "
"your GPU support in Dom0 in the first place (by using a different kernel), "
"or install Qubes OS on a different system."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/3_0/release-notes.rst:41
#: fda16f9814624ceeb4a238cf75e52511
msgid ""
"For other known issues take a look at `our tickets "
"<https://github.com/QubesOS/qubes-"
"issues/issues?q=is%3Aopen+is%3Aissue+milestone%3A%22Release+3.0%22+label%3Abug>`__"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/3_0/release-notes.rst:45
#: abb33219de744dd1b6ec1cb95d161ac9
msgid ""
"It is advised to install updates just after system installation to apply bug"
" fixes for (some of) the above problems."
msgstr ""

