msgid "From R3.0 release candidate"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/3_0/release-notes.rst:67
#: 85523b70348b40fabe59e3dea78c4641
msgid ""
"If you are using Qubes R3.0rc1, R3.0rc2 or R3.0rc3, just install system "
"updates, there is no special steps required."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/3_0/release-notes.rst:70
