msgid "From R2.0 or earlier"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/3_0/release-notes.rst:73
#: 03ed8ef6d4034ca5bfeb256497a44c15
msgid ""
"The easiest and safest way to upgrade to Qubes R3.0 is to install it from "
"scratch and use :doc:`qubes backup and restore tools </user/how-to-"
"guides/how-to-back-up-restore-and-migrate>` for migrating of all of the user"
" VMs."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/3_0/release-notes.rst:75
#: e128d2991e28433dace1732bcd86e801
msgid ""
